Package NaturalLanguageApi.RdfGenObjects.CreationParts

Class Summary
RdfEdge Class that represents an RDF edge (edge-id, rdf-type, node-id to which it points) in RDF format
RdfNode Class that represents an RDF node (old/new node, rdf-type, node-id, edge array) in RDF format
RdfPatternRepeatMode Abstract Class for representing all of the repetition modes
RdfRepeatConst Class that represents a constant value that will be used repetition mode
RdfRepeatRange Class that represents a range value that will be used repetition mode
